<div class="section-container cutin-top-alt cutout-bottom">
  <section class="section" id="ecosystem">
  <div class="container">
    <h2 class="section-title deep-lavender has-text-centered">Ecosystem overview</h2>
    <h3 class="dark-indigo has-text-centered">Every stakeholder benefits from collective value creation through development of Ecosystem V</h3>
        <div class="columns is-vcentered">
            <div class="column is-7">
                <img src="/assets/radial-slider.svg">
            </div>
            <div class="column">
            <div class="gradient-card">
                <div class="content">
                    <h3 class="title subsection-title dark-indigo">Marketplace</h3>
                    <p class="muted">Marketplaces have become common on the internet, yet a useful plug-and-play marketplace for blockchain solutions hasn’t been created. Connect your apps and automate processes in our marketplace in minutes. </p>
