                </div>
            </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</div>

<div class="section-container">
  <section class="section alt p-top-l p-bottom-l neg-m-top-m">
    <div class="section-body">
  <div class="container is-vcentered">
    <div class="columns">
    <div class="column is-5-desktop">
      <h2 class="section-title deep-lavender">The network effect</h2>
        <div class="content">
      <p class="column-left-text steel">
          We don’t live with the illusion that we can make adoption happen by ourselves. It’s about the community as much as it’s about network users. Learn more about how you can contribute to the ecosystem.
