<div class="section-container cutin-top-alt cutout-bottom-alt">
  <section class="section p-top-xl p-bottom-xxl alt">
    <div class="section-body">
      <div class="container">
        <h2 class="section-title has-text-centered">
          Testimonials
        </h2>
          <div class="columns is-centered">
              <div class="column is-5">
                  <div class="card testimonial-eco">
                  <div class="testimonial-logo">
                      <img src="/assets/use-cases/capptions@2x.png">
                  </div>
                  <div class="content">
                      <p class="muted">"We believe that a user should be educated on what blockchain is and how it adds value in day-to-day operations. By integrating LTO Network’s anchoring service across the Capptions platform, we are able to give blockchain a mobile face."
                      </p>
                  </div>
                      <div class="btn-container has-text-centered">
                          <a href="/use-cases/capptions/" class="button is-primary">Explore use case</a>
                      </div>
                  </div>
              </div>
              <div class="column is-1 is-hidden-mobile"></div>
              <div class="column is-5">
                  <div class="card testimonial-eco">
                  <div class="testimonial-logo">
                      <img src="/assets/use-cases/signrequest@2x.png">
                  </div>
                  <div class="content">
                      <p class="muted">"We experimented with document time stamping through multiple blockchains. However if we wanted to include the blockchain timestamp proof in the log of the signed document we required instant verification. With LTO Network we can add instant immutability to the documents being signed on our platform."
                      </p>
                  </div>
                      <div class="btn-container has-text-centered">
                          <a href="/use-cases/signrequest/" class="button is-primary">Explore use case</a>
                      </div>
                  </div>
              </div>
          </div>
      </div>
      </div>
  </section>
</div>

